22
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:10,880
You bought all their pearls.

23
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,560
With this,

24
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,840
your Li family dominates Hepu’s pearl trade.

25
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:16,120
