59
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,000
What should we do?

60
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:22,080
I searched so hard.

61
00:03:22,080 --> 00:03:22,800
I’ve looked everywhere.

62
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:23,840
