90
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,040
Someone!

91
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:10,400
Open all the shells for me.

92
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:15,960
Come on, come on.

93
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,120
These pearls of ours

94
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:26,240
